OL,3,GBLOOPERSCPower failure during UEFA
OL,4,CChampions League match disrupts BBC Two
OL,5,Ccoverage
OL,6,
OL,7,FBBC Two's live coverage of the UEFA
OL,8,FWomen's Champions League match between
OL,9,FChelsea and Barcelona was disrupted for
OL,10,Fabout ten minutes this evening due to a
OL,11,Fpower failure at the stadium.
OL,13,FAlmost 35 minutes into the match,
OL,14,Fvision and audio cut out, quickly
OL,15,Ffollowed by the appearance of colour
OL,16,Fbars.
OL,18,FAbout ten seconds later, BBC Two
OL,19,Finvoked its breakdown procedure and the
OL,20,Fchannel's standard breakdown caption
OL,21,Fappeared.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
