OL,3,GBLOOPERSCPower failure during UEFA
OL,4,CChampions League match disrupts BBC Two
OL,5,Ccoverage
OL,6,
OL,7,FOn Network BBC Two, the graphic
OL,8,Fremained on screen animating in silence
OL,9,Ffor almost a minute-and-a-half before
OL,10,Fthe announcer arrived, offering an
OL,11,Fapology and cued some music.
OL,13,FAfter about eight minutes of breakdown,
OL,14,Fthe announcer told us there had been a
OL,15,Fpower failure at the stadium.
OL,17,FThe music then continued for another
OL,18,Fminute or so. The announcer then
OL,19,Finformed us that live coverage would
OL,20,Fnow resume.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
