OL,3,GBLOOPERSCPower failure during UEFA
OL,4,CChampions League match disrupts BBC Two
OL,5,Ccoverage
OL,6,
OL,7,FAnd so it did. In fact, the match had
OL,8,Fbeen stopped due to the power issues,
OL,9,Fso viewers at home didn't miss too much
OL,10,Fof the action.
OL,12,FBBC Two Wales took the first 25 seconds
OL,13,Fof the Network breakdown before going
OL,14,Fin circuit and covering the remainder
OL,15,Fof the breakdown.
OL,17,FThe BBC Wales announcer provided a
OL,18,Fverbal apology on a regular basis and
OL,19,Fkept viewers informed about what was
OL,20,Fgoing on behind the scenes.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
