OL,3,GBLOOPERSCPower failure during UEFA
OL,4,CChampions League match disrupts BBC Two
OL,5,Ccoverage
OL,6,
OL,7,FOver on BBC Two Northern Ireland, a
OL,8,Fsomewhat odd sequence of events.
OL,10,FThey took the Network breakdown for the
OL,11,Ffirst 30 seconds or so.
OL,13,FIt then looks as though they went in
OL,14,Fcircuit, showing the stadium output
OL,15,F(just a black screen but with audio of
OL,16,Fsome sort), plus a branded 'Temporary
OL,17,FFault' lower-third.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
