OL,3,GBLOOPERSCPower failure during UEFA
OL,4,CChampions League match disrupts BBC Two
OL,5,Ccoverage
OL,6,
OL,7,FThey then cut to a loop of a generic,
OL,8,Fanimated BBC Two Northern Ireland logo,
OL,9,Fwhich remained for over four-and-a-half
OL,10,Fminutes, with an occasional verbal
OL,11,Fapology from the announcer.
OL,13,FThe 'Temporary Fault' lower-third put
OL,14,Fin another brief appearance also.
OL,16,FWe then got a few seconds of the
OL,17,Fstadium output again, before crashing
OL,18,Fback to the Network breakdown.
